text: The Downfall (, ) is a 1961 Greek drama movie directed by Giannis Dalianidis and starring Zoe Laskari, Nikos Kourkoulos, Vangelis Voulgaridis, Pantelis Zervos, Kostas Voutsas. ==Other websites== * Category:1961 drama movies Category:Greek movies Category:Movies directed by Giannis Dalianidis
